<!-- Banner -->
<div class="banner-peetayers" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,168,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url('<%=image_path "https://source.unsplash.com/collection/865018/1000x300"%>');">
  <div class="banner-peetayers-content">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- End Banner -->

<div class="container">
  <div class="body">
    <div class="row">

      <div class="column-1">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3">
          <div class="polaroid flo">
            <div class="polaroid-img" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/32438091?v=4');">
            </div>
            <p class="polaroid-text"><strong>Florine, 28 ans<strong></p>
            <p class="polaroid-desc">"I know Lille inside out!"</p>
          </div>
          <br>

          <div class="infos">
            <div class="infos-title text-center">
              <p><strong>Information checked</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="infos-content">
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Official ID</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Phone</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Email</p></ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="column-2">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9">

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space1 text-center">
                <div class="space1-title">
                  <h3>Hello, I'm Florine!</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="space1-content">
                  <p>Lille, France Â° since 6 years</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Available services</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/suitcase.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Prepare your trip</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/location.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Housing services</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/medical-history.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Help with admins</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/chat.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Speak local</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/cheers.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Local tips</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/masks.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Cultural outings</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/football.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Play sports</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/welcome.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Be welcomed</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Languages?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>French, English & Spanish</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Why do you like Lille?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Lille is a very nice and friendly city, neither too big nor too small. You can't be bored, there is always something to do.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Your favorite spots in Lille?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>The "Vieux Lille" (old city) with its many beautiful streets.  There are lot of bars very cosy and cool. An other spot very nice to walk is "La Citadelle", a very peacefull park.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Why do you want to become a Peetayer?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>To help and meet new people. Share my experience and local tips in Lille. I know what it's like to arrive in a new city and I enjoyed being helped by locals and expatriates. My turn to do the same.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>What are your interests?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>I really like going out with my friends for a drink. But also different and cultural outings like going to the theater, go to concerts, museum...</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>What about Florine?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Florine studied in Lille, and after some years in Paris and abroad, she came back in the "Vieux Lille" (old town). Young entrepreneur, she likes meet new people, in particular strangers to share with them the local culture, speak english and spanish, and to discover the beautiful city of Lille.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Which countries have you visited?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Spain, Brazil, Canada, US, UK, Portugal, Cambodia, Vietnam, Malaysia, Italy</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

